A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Lawrence J. "Doc" Cohen; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Lawrence J. "Doc" Cohen is a pioneering entrepreneur and franchise leader who
3 founded Deblan Corporation and Cookie Associates, developing 35 Great American Cookie
4 Company (GACC) units across seven states and operating eight of the top ten
5 highest-volume stores in the chain; and
6 WHEREAS, he played a key role in the growth and success of the Great American Cookie
7 Company franchise system, serving as the founding president of its Franchise Advisory
8 Council and co-founding the Independent Association of Great American Cookie
9 Franchisees, where he serves as a permanent member of the Executive Committee; and
10 WHEREAS, he has demonstrated exceptional leadership within the International Franchise
11 Association (IFA), serving as its treasurer for five years and earning distinction as the second
12 franchisee in history to serve as chairman of its Board of Directors; and
13 WHEREAS, he was the first franchisee in the world to earn the designation of Certified
14 Franchise Executive from the IFA Educational Foundation and has served as a trustee, chair
